{
  "stem": "22391.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He didn't have his children, and they throw him out of his job, because eventually they find out that he was helping Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he got punished in a way, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't want it to create more trouble for him, so I didn't want he should have to bother with me that he had more hard time down there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you went back to Germany, to Landsberg, what were you hoping would happen next?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that point, I know I have to start a life on my own, because there's really nobody for me to be.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't want hang around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got married, because I thought he was a better way to belong to somebody than to just to be by myself.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't want to do anything without my parents knowing it, that I'm getting married, because I know him before already from Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I just felt I, I need approval, but I didn't get it, because there was nobody around.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Landsberg, in 1946.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we really didn't had a life until we came to America, because--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, because that American soldiers did find my family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they find from my father's side here the [NON-ENGLISH] in Bridgeport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if you heard of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from my mother's side-- my mother was a [NON-ENGLISH] girl, so they find from London, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And matter of fact, in Germany, they sent somebody, one of the-- he was in the Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a rabbi for America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they contact him to come and visit me in Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came, and he give me $20.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
